The paper deals with social image retrieval, which involves the use of tags to retrieve images. This falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of visual content in conjunction with tags, which suggests that it may fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of supervised and unsupervised methods, which suggests that it may fall under machine learning (cs.CL) and social networks (cs.SI).
